				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Ph%C3%BA-Th%E1%BB%A9/B%E1%BB%87nh-kh%E1%BB%9Fi-h%E1%BB%89-t%C3%ACnh/poem-bNZy2kl1ozFG_-JT48TnOg">Bệnh khởi hỉ tình - 病起喜晴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Ph%C3%BA-Th%E1%BB%A9/author-cJyRnXqV8KjQY5jLmb3KOA">Phạm Phú Thứ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/D%C3%A3-v%E1%BB%8Dng-N%E1%BA%A1p-n%E1%BA%A1p-c%C3%A0n-kh%C3%B4n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i/poem-IKc7EODoeBqyyW7VYjZl5Q">Dã vọng (Nạp nạp càn khôn đại) - 野望（納納乾坤大）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/%C4%90%E1%BA%AFc-Cam-L%E1%BB%99-lai-th%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%B7-ph%C3%BA/poem-5tmMyTOrWH5VPiFI5iRXaw">Đắc Cam Lộ lai thư hỷ phú - 得甘露來書喜賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-k7nDOMHcGKaZoky6ue8-ag">Nguyễn Thượng Hiền</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Qu%C3%A2n/Kh%E1%BB%91c-Hoa-Kh%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-nh%E1%BA%A5t-b%C3%A1ch-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-034/poem-xmr0EhuOQLtTSv1k-RLKxQ">Khốc Hoa Khương nhất bách thủ kỳ 034 - 哭華姜一百首其三十四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Qu%C3%A2n/author-Uj_DhxmeC-SDbSqFUZOc6w">Khuất Đại Quân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BB%99ng-L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-t3J6Fcmdaf3mpdvJwS2fsg">Mộng Lý Bạch kỳ 1 - 夢李白其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/T%C3%A2n-qu%C3%A1n-ng%E1%BB%A5-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%E1%BB%B3-15/poem-ZzibyZU3uWiwUYBRDFmI8w">Tân quán ngụ hứng kỳ 15 - 津觀寓興其十五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-Rv6locqJPIunovJpeqDNxA">Nguyễn Bỉnh Khiêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Thanh-nh%C3%A2n-2/poem-UsDuyCrOt5wTDMLmGJREJA">Thanh nhân 2 - 清人 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-B%E1%BB%99i-Ch%C3%A2u/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-nSdTCVcuclUg3EtZ-RVF2w">Thu dạ đối nguyệt - 秋夜對月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-B%E1%BB%99i-Ch%C3%A2u/author-n3IODPoQwb1NxPzORIY_Uw">Phan Bội Châu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BB%A5c-th%E1%BB%B1c-nh%E1%BA%ADt-th%E1%BB%8B-T%C3%B4ng-V%C4%83n-T%C3%B4ng-V%C5%A9/poem-54S-W7WU58SBjagCRp5hdQ">Thục thực nhật thị Tông Văn, Tông Vũ - 熟食日示宗文、宗武</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/U-s%E1%BA%A7u-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-Dv6CCYTTwuCJ7Z2hI0opMQ">U sầu kỳ 2 - 幽愁其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
